# Program Images Directory

Place custom program images here.

## Usage
Add the `image` field to any program in `_data/programs/*.yml`:

```yaml
- id: example-program
  name: Example Program
  category: Recreation
  image: /assets/images/programs/example-program.jpg  # <-- Add this line
  # ... other fields ...
```

## Recommended Image Specs
- Aspect ratio: 16:9 or similar landscape
- Minimum size: 400x225 pixels
- Formats: JPG, PNG, WebP
- Keep file size under 100KB for performance

## Fallback
If no image is provided, the card displays a category-colored gradient with an icon.
